!! Sub-brain architecture: file delegation and category loading
Reason: Core design decision — sub-brains create distributed data minds. Root files.brain links .pinky/ folders, never files inside them. BOOT step 8 resolves categories by checking each sub-brain's overview.brain for relevance before loading. Sub-brain wins for scope-local decisions, root wins cross-cutting.
